title: Underdogs
overview: Anything can happen when seven celebrities and their dogs are thrown onto the agility course. Those competing are Anders Bagge, NicoleFalciani, DoggeDoggelito, Theoz, Johanna Lind Bagge, Klara Doktorow and Christian "Kicken" Lundqvist.
